sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ImageAPI as ImageStream API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,ImageAPI: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access
    User->>Route: GET /<br/>No Auth
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS (TLS reencrypt)
    OAuth->>OAuthServer: OAuth redirect<br/>Client Credentials
    OAuthServer-->>OAuth: OAuth Token (JWT)
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    Backend-->>OAuth: Dashboard HTML/JS
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Kubernetes API Interaction (Create Notebook)
    User->>Route: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: POST notebooks<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR created
    Backend-->>OAuth: Success Response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Notebook created

    Note over Backend,Thanos: Flow 3: Metrics Query
    User->>Route: GET /api/prometheus<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080
    Backend->>Thanos: GET /api/v1/query<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics data (JSON)
    Backend-->>OAuth: Metrics response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Metrics displayed

    Note over Backend,ImageAPI: Flow 4: Image Metadata Retrieval
    User->>Route: GET /api/images<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: HTTP/8080
    Backend->>ImageAPI: GET imagestreams/layers<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ImageAPI-->>Backend: Image metadata
    Backend-->>OAuth: Image list
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Available images
